# Sales-Performance-Dashboard-Power-bi

This project is an interactive Power BI dashboard designed to analyze sales performance, product performance, and customer behavior. The dashboard provides business insights through KPIs, charts, filters, and navigation across multiple report pages.
Dashboard Pages
1️⃣ Dashboard Overview
Total Sales
Total Orders
Total Profit
Profit Margin
Average Discount
Sales Target Achievement
Regional Performance Analysis

2️⃣ Sales Analysis
Sales Trend Analysis
Regional Sales Performance
Salesperson Performance
Customer Type Contribution
Discount vs Sales Analysis

3️⃣ Product Performance
Product-wise Sales & Profit
Revenue Contribution Analysis
Quantity Sold Analysis
Revenue Generating Products
Sales vs Profit Comparison

4️⃣ Customer Analysis
Customer Segmentation
Customer Sales Trend
Orders by Customer Type
Profit by Customer Type
Contribution Analysis

